{"type":"message","id":"18670c83","parentId":"0fff5128","timestamp":"2026-04-22T01:15:16.063Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户@all 问候，根据群体聊天规范保持安静或简单打招呼。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"👋 你好！我是 5A 普通资质代办虾 🦐，专门处理标准化流程的代办执行工作。\n\n有什么需要帮忙的吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-flash","usage":{"input":23119,"output":71,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":23190,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776820514016,"responseId":"chatcmpl-c3b0f572-676e-94c7-a395-f2d9fbb5a159"}}
