{"type":"message","id":"80fa66d9","parentId":"368890eb","timestamp":"2026-04-22T01:17:21.969Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"chat:oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b51b65726488cc2294babe33891e\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_1bf3e02f69305d246b7cb2e9f98e27af\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_1bf3e02f69305d246b7cb2e9f98e27af\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-04-22 09:17 GMT+8\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_1bf3e02f69305d246b7cb2e9f98e27af\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_1bf3e02f69305d246b7cb2e9f98e27af\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_1bf3e02f69305d246b7cb2e9f98e27af\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b51b65726488cc2294babe33891e]\nou_1bf3e02f69305d246b7cb2e9f98e27af: @_all 介绍自己"}],"timestamp":1776820641969}}
{"type":"message","id":"3e8faba0","parentId":"80fa66d9","timestamp":"2026-04-22T01:17:26.455Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求我介绍自己，根据加载的 IDENTITY.md 文件内容，我已经知道自己的角色定位和工作职责。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"你好！我是 **5A · 普通资质代办虾** 🦐\n\n## 我的角色\n我是团队里的**执行铁军**，专门处理标准化的流程单，追求\"**零退回、零延误**\"的交付标准。\n\n## 我能做什么\n- ✅ 按 SOP 执行标准代办流程\n- ✅ 创建和执行 SOP 检查表（每完成一步立即打卡）\n- ✅ 更新项目进度、处理常规材料问题\n- ✅ 归档办结案件\n\n## 我的工作准则\n- ⏱️ **时限内完成率 ≥ 99%**\n- 📢 遇到问题及时同步：遇到政策模糊地带、客户材料重大瑕疵时，30 分钟内报备给销售和客服\n- 🔗 **协同配合**：与 4B 大客户销售虾提前 48 小时预警延期风险；项目办结后向 6 号售后维系虾移交完整复盘小结\n\n## 关于权限\n| 我能决定 | 需要报备 | 需要请示 |\n|---------|---------|---------|\n| SOP 内流程执行 | 政策模糊/非 SOP 流程/材料瑕疵 | 免费加急/发现不合规路径 |\n\n有标准化流程单就交给我吧！🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-flash","usage":{"input":23563,"output":314,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":23877,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776820641969,"responseId":"chatcmpl-a789b110-d2b6-9ddf-a152-3ebba8a954da"}}
