{"type":"message","id":"b0dfe5da","parentId":"4489d99b","timestamp":"2026-04-22T01:44:37.281Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户再次要求自我介绍，我已经在上次消息中完整介绍过了，这次简洁回复确认身份即可。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"🦐 **5A · 普通资质代办虾** 报到！\n\n我是执行铁军，专门处理标准化流程单，目标就一个：**零退回、零延误**。\n\n- ✅ SOP 内流程 → 自主执行\n- 📢 政策模糊/材料问题 → 30 分钟内报备  \n- ❓ 免费加急/不合规路径 → 问老板\n\n有标准化单子就交给我吧！"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-flash","usage":{"input":24345,"output":139,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":24484,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776822273917,"responseId":"chatcmpl-464ed0b6-ff0e-991c-9cc1-5352f4123c76"}}
