2                       # 切换到标签页 2\n+495 agent-browser frame @e5                   # 进入 iframe\n+496 agent-browser frame main                  # 返回主文档\n+497 ```\n+498 \n+499 #### 最佳实践\n+500 1. **始终使用 `-i` 标志** - 只关注可交互元素\n+501 2. **始终使用 `--json`** - 便于解析\n+502 3. **等待稳定性** - `agent-browser wait --load networkidle`\n+503 4. **保存认证状态** - 用 `state save/load` 跳过登录流程\n+504 5. **使用会话** - 隔离不同的浏览器上下文\n+505 6. **调试时用 `--headed`** - 可视化看到操作过程\n+506 \n+507 #### Snapshot JSON 格式示例\n+508 ```json\n+509 {\n+510   \"success\": true,\n+511   \"data\": {\n+512     \"snapshot\": \"...\",\n+513     \"refs\": {\n+514       \"e1\": {\"role\": \"heading\", \"name\": \"Example Domain\"},\n+515       \"e2\": {\"role\": \"button\", \"name\": \"Submit\"},\n+516       \"e3\": {\"role\": \"textbox\", \"name\": \"Email\"}\n+517     }\n+518   }\n+519 }\n+520 ```","firstChangedLine":376},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776836760926}}
{"type":"message","id":"52e012f8","parentId":"381f6254","timestamp":"2026-04-22T05:46:14.118Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"成功保存到 MEMORY.md 后，需要向用户确认已完成并简要总结技能的核心要点。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"✅ **已保存到记忆！**\n\n已将 `agent-browser` 技能用法完整记录到 `MEMORY.md`，包括：\n\n### 🌐 agent-browser 浏览器自动化技能核心要点\n\n**目录**: `/Users/zhu/.openclaw/workspace/skills/agent-browser-clawdbot`\n\n#### 使用场景对比\n- ✅ **用 agent-browser**: 多步骤自动化、确定元素选择、性能关键、SPA 处理、会话隔离\n- ❌ **用内置 browser 工具**: 需要截图/PDF、视觉检查、扩展集成\n\n#### 核心工作流\n```bash\n1. agent-browser open <url>\n2. agent-browser snapshot -i --json     # 获取 refs\n3. agent-browser click @e2             # 通过 ref 交互\n4. agent-browser snapshot -i --json     # 重新快照\n```\n\n#### 关键命令速览\n| 类型 | 示例 |\n|------|------|\n| 导航 | `agent-browser open https://...` |\n| 快照 | `agent-browser snapshot -i --json` |\n| 点击 | `agent-browser click @e2` |\n| 填充 | `agent-browser fill @e3 \"text\"` |\n| 等待 | `agent-browser wait --load networkidle` |\n| 会话 | `--session admin/user` |\n| 保存状态 | `state save/load auth.json` |\n\n以后遇到需要浏览器自动化操作的任务，我会调用这个技能！🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-flash","usage":{"input":45880,"output":362,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":46242,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776836760928,"responseId":"chatcmpl-2b398663-8453-9fa3-8efb-745be08824fb"}}
