{"type":"message","id":"a7d1dfbc","parentId":"34795d06","timestamp":"2026-04-22T06:46:22.805Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"已完成技能内容的保存，现在需要向用户确认并总结这个 Skill 查找器的核心要点。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"✅ **已保存到记忆！**\n\n已将 `skill-finder-cn` 技能完整记录到 `MEMORY.md`。\n\n### 🔍 Skill 查找器核心要点\n\n**目录**: `/Users/zhu/.openclaw/workspace/skills/skill-finder-cn`  \n**触发词**: 找 skill、find skill、搜索 skill、有什么 skill 可以...\n\n#### 核心功能\n当用户询问需要什么 skill 时，帮助搜索 ClawHub 并推荐相关 Skills。\n\n#### 关键命令\n```bash\nclawhub search \"<需求>\"     # 搜索\nclawhub inspect <name>      # 查看详情\nclawhub install <name>      # 安装\nls ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/  # 验证安装\nclawhub list                # 查看已安装列表\n```\n\n#### 工作流程\n1. 理解需求 → 2. 提取关键词 → 3. 搜索 ClawHub → 4. 列出结果（下载量/stars） → 5. 推荐 → 6. 安装后验证\n\n#### 输出格式规范\n每个搜索结果包含：\n- ✅ Skill 名称\n- ✅ 中文描述\n- ✅ 下载量 & Stars\n- ✅ 是否已安装标记\n\n以后当我需要帮你查找合适的 Skill 时，我会使用这个技能！🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-flash","usage":{"input":52311,"output":327,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":52638,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776840379667,"responseId":"chatcmpl-9c67417b-0904-943a-9c8c-1cff0c754582"}}
